    "subtype": "weapon",
    "text": "A heavy, weighted cube of metal at the end of a long chain, the dorn-dergar is used by dwarven berserkers and sappers who specialize in breaking through lines of shielded opponents or disabling enemy siege weapons.",
    "traits": [
      {
        "alternate_link": {
